?><!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en-nz"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" /><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><title>Shoreline Cinema Waikanae</title><meta name="description" content="Shoreline Cinema is Waikanae's premiere cinema complex. Find out who we are, what's on, what's coming up, how to contact us and much more."><link href="/tpl/inc/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><link href="/tpl/inc/css/print.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="print" /><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/tpl/inc/css/slick.css"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/tpl/inc/css/slick-theme.css"/></head><body><header><div class="box-auto hide show-med"><img src="/tpl/inc/img/sl_logo.png" class="img-responsive mc-auto show"></div><nav><a class="logo hide-med" href="#"><img src="/tpl/inc/img/sl_logo.png" height="25"></a><button class="hide-med" type="button"><span class="icon-text">Menu&nbsp;</span><span class="icon"></span></button><div class="collapse jc-center" id="navbar"><ul class="nav-links"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="/home/">HOME</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/whats-on-today/">WHAT&apos;S ON TODAY</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/whats-on/">WHAT&apos;S ON</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/coming-soon/">COMING SOON</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/venue-hire/">VENUE HIRE</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/about-us/">ABOUT US</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/contact-us/">CONTACT US</a></li></ul></div></nav></header><div class="wrapper">
<div class="featured"><div class="content"><div class="featured-carousel"><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/37-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="The Peanut Butter Falcon Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">The Peanut Butter Falcon</h1><p>The Peanut Butter Falcon is a prison break movie and Western where horses and desert prairie are replaced with crab boats, rafts & sand islands. It's a Southern living in the world of a modern Mark Twain that begins when Zak, a 22-year-old young man with Down syndrome runs away from a nursing home to chase his dream of becoming a professional wrestler by attending the wrestling school of The Salt Water Redneck. Through circumstances beyond their control Tyler (29), a small time outlaw on the run becomes Zak's unlikely wrestling coach and ally, and together they wind through deltas & marshes, elude capture, drink whisky, find God, catch fish, and convince Eleanor (27) a beautiful nursing home employee to join them on their journey rather than returning Zak to his previous life.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/37/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/44-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="The Gentlemen Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">The Gentlemen</h1><p>Mickey Pearson is an American expatriate who became rich by building a marijuana empire in London. When word gets out that he's looking to cash out of the business, it soon triggers an array of plots and schemes from those who want his fortune.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/44/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/36-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Cats Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Cats</h1><p>A tribe of cats called the Jellicles must decide yearly which one will ascend to the Heaviside Layer and come back to a new Jellicle life.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/36/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/38-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Van Gogh & Japan Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Van Gogh & Japan</h1><p>In this little known story of Van Goghâ€™s art we see just how important his study of Japan was. The film travels not only to France and the Netherlands but also to Japan to further explore the remarkable heritage that so affected Van Gogh and made him the artist we know of today.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/38/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/31-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Ford v Ferrari Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Ford v Ferrari</h1><p>American car designer Carroll Shelby and driver Ken Miles battle corporate interference, the laws of physics and their own personal demons to build a revolutionary race car for Ford and challenge Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans in 1966.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/31/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/42-small-custom.jpg" width="150" alt="Happy New Year, Colin Burstead Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Happy New Year, Colin Burstead</h1><p>Colin hires a lavish country manor for his extended family to celebrate New Year. Unfortunately for Colin his position of power in the family is under serious threat from the arrival of his estranged brother David.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/42/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/46-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Frozen II Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Frozen II</h1><p>Anna, Elsa, Kristoff, Olaf and Sven leave Arendelle to travel to an ancient, autumn-bound forest of an enchanted land. They set out to find the origin of Elsa's powers in order to save their kingdom.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/46/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/24-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Knives Out Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Knives Out</h1><p>When renowned crime novelist Harlan Thrombey (Christopher Plummer) is found dead at his estate just after his 85th birthday, the inquisitive and debonair Detective Benoit Blanc (Daniel Craig) is mysteriously enlisted to investigate. From Harlan's dysfunctional family to his devoted staff, Blanc sifts through a web of red herrings and self-serving lies to uncover the truth behind Harlan's untimely death.

Genre: Comedy, Crime, Drama
Stars: Chris Evans, Ana de Armas, Daniel Craig, Daniel Redcliff</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/24/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/40-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Little Women Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Little Women</h1><p>Four sisters come of age in America in the aftermath of the Civil War.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/40/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/29-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="The Good Liar Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">The Good Liar</h1><p>Career con artist Roy Courtnay can hardly believe his luck when he meets well-to-do widow Betty McLeish online. As Betty opens her home and life to him, Roy is surprised to find himself caring about her, turning what should be a cut-and-dry swindle into the most treacherous tightrope walk of his life.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/29/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/34-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Ask Dr. Ruth Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Ask Dr. Ruth</h1><p>As her 90th birthday approaches, Dr. Ruth Westheimer reflects on her painful past. A survivor of the Holocaust, her career path leads her to the forefront of the sexual revolution, making her America's most famous sex therapist.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/34/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/39-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="1917 Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">1917</h1><p>Two young British privates during the First World War are given an impossible mission: deliver a message deep in enemy territory that will stop 1,600 men, and one of the soldier's brothers, from walking straight into a deadly trap.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/39/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/41-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Sorry We Missed You Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Sorry We Missed You</h1><p>A hard-up delivery driver and his wife struggle to get by in modern-day England.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/41/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/28-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="The Biggest Little Farm Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">The Biggest Little Farm</h1><p>The Biggest Little Farm is a 2018 American documentary film, directed by Emmy Award Winning director John Chester. The film profiles Chester and his wife Molly as they acquire and establish themselves on Apricot Lane Farms in Moorpark, California.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/28/">See More</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="information"><div class="content"><div class="content-wrapper"><div class="box"><h2>Opening Hours</h2>
